'''籃上干擾'''(basket interference)是指在進攻時若球仍處於攻方的籃框圓柱或已碰籃板上，進攻球員觸球而犯規。<ref>[http://www.ncaapublications.com/DownloadPublication.aspx?download=BR11.pdf 2009-2011 Men's & Women's Basketball Rules] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncaapublications.com/DownloadPublication.aspx?download=BR11.pdf |date=20120806220855 }} Rule 4, Section 5, Article 2. Retrieved July 27, 2010</ref><ref>[http://i.cdn.turner.com/nba/nba/.element/pdf/2.0/sect/officiating/Official_NBA_Rule_Rook_09-10.pdf NBA Official Rules (2009-2010)] {{Wayback|url=http://i.cdn.turner.com/nba/nba/.element/pdf/2.0/sect/officiating/Official_NBA_Rule_Rook_09-10.pdf |date=20120111152818 }} Rule 11, Section I, a, b, f, and h. Retrieved July 27, 2010</ref>但若直接[[灌籃|灌籃]]、則不算籃上干擾。

由於性質類似，籃上干擾亦被稱為進攻版的[[妨礙中籃|妨礙中籃]](offensive goal tending)。

